<p><a name="Organizations_working_on_the_issue" id="Organizations_working_on_the_issue"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sweatshop&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Organizations working on the issue">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Organizations working on the issue</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Clean_Clothes_Campaign" title="Clean Clothes Campaign">Clean Clothes Campaign</a> international alliance of labour unions and non-governmental organizations</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/International_Labor_Rights_Fund" title="International Labor Rights Fund" class="mw-redirect">International Labor Rights Fund</a></li>
