<li><a href="/wiki/National_Labor_Committee" title="National Labor Committee" class="mw-redirect">National Labor Committee</a> founded to combat sweatshop labor and US government policy in El Salvador and Central America.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Green_America" title="Green America">Green America</a> membership organization based in the United States</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Students_%26_Scholars_Against_Corporate_Misbehavior&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Students &amp; Scholars Against Corporate Misbehavior (page does not exist)">Students &amp; Scholars Against Corporate Misbehavior</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/United_Students_Against_Sweatshops" title="United Students Against Sweatshops">United Students Against Sweatshops</a> a student organization in the United States and Canada</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Woo_Harry&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Woo Harry (page does not exist)">Woo Harry</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Free_the_Children" title="Free the Children">Free the Children</a> A Canadian Organization that helps raise awareness and put a stop to Child Labour - Also helps other children in need.</li>
</ul>
