<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sweatshop&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: See also">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">See also</span></h2>
<table class="navbox" cellspacing="0" style=";">
<tr>
<td style="padding:2px;">
<table cellspacing="0" class="nowraplinks collapsible autocollapse" style="width:100%;background:transparent;color:inherit;;">
<tr>
