<li><a href="http://home.sandiego.edu/~mzwolinski/Sweatshops_essay_web.pdf" class="external text" title="http://home.sandiego.edu/~mzwolinski/Sweatshops_essay_web.pdf" rel="nofollow">Matt Zwolinski on the definition, history, and morality of sweatshops</a></li>
<li><a href="http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=901689" class="external text" title="http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=901689" rel="nofollow">Academic Paper: "Sweatshops, Choice, and Exploitation"</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/library/magazine/home/20000924mag-sweatshops.html" class="external text" title="http://www.nytimes.com/library/magazine/home/20000924mag-sweatshops.html" rel="nofollow">Two Cheers for Sweatshops</a> - <i><a href="/wiki/New_York_Times" title="New York Times" class="mw-redirect">New York Times</a></i>, by <a href="/wiki/Nicholas_Kristof" title="Nicholas Kristof" class="mw-redirect">Nicholas Kristof</a> and <a href="/wiki/Sheryl_WuDunn" title="Sheryl WuDunn">Sheryl WuDunn</a></li>
<li><a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20060210100127/http://www.prospect.org/print/V10/46/dreier-p.html" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20060210100127/http://www.prospect.org/print/V10/46/dreier-p.html" rel="nofollow">The Campus Sweatshop Movement</a> - <a href="/wiki/American_Prospect" title="American Prospect" class="mw-redirect">American Prospect</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.extension.umn.edu/extensionnews/2000/ForeignOwnedBusinessesInVietnam.html" class="external text" title="http://www.extension.umn.edu/extensionnews/2000/ForeignOwnedBusinessesInVietnam.html" rel="nofollow">"Foreign owned businesses in Vietnam aren't sweatshops"</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ilr.cornell.edu/trianglefire/photos/photo_enlargements.html?image_id=62&amp;sec_id=8" class="external text" title="http://www.ilr.cornell.edu/trianglefire/photos/photo_enlargements.html?image_id=62&amp;sec_id=8" rel="nofollow">Triangle Fire: Photographs</a> from the <a href="/wiki/Triangle_Shirtwaist_Factory_fire" title="Triangle Shirtwaist Factory fire">Triangle Shirtwaist Factory fire</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ihscslnews.org" class="external text" title="http://www.ihscslnews.org" rel="nofollow">Immaculata High School Child Slave Labor News</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.dollarsandsense.org/archives/2005/0905blair.html" class="external text" title="http://www.dollarsandsense.org/archives/2005/0905blair.html" rel="nofollow">Article on worker takeover of sweatshop in El Salvador</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.dollarsandsense.org/archives/2006/0906miller.html" class="external text" title="http://www.dollarsandsense.org/archives/2006/0906miller.html" rel="nofollow">Economist John Miller on sweatshops</a> in <i><a href="/wiki/Dollars_%26_Sense" title="Dollars &amp; Sense">Dollars &amp; Sense</a></i></li>
<li>[<a href="http://www.msmagazine.com/spring2006/paradise_full.asp" class="external free" title="http://www.msmagazine.com/spring2006/paradise_full.asp" rel="nofollow">http://www.msmagazine.com/spring2006/paradise_full.asp</a> Paradise Lost: sweatshop labor on the U.S. island of Saipan</li>
</ul>


